source.name: 2005-2009 BBG Key Performance Indicators
source.description: To increase accountability, the BBG has published its Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) for FY 2005 through FY 2009.  KPIs include audience and affiliate network sizes and program quality and credibility ratings for each of the BBG's broadcasters.
